<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>快乐早餐</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/base.css">
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <a href="javascript:history.back(-1);"><img src="images/back.png" alt=""></a>
    <p>申请退款</p>
</header>

<div class="body_box return_money">
    <div class="top">
        <p>请您选择或说明原因，我们会及时为您处理</p>
        <p>给您带来不好的体验，我们非常抱歉</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="que_list">
        <li values="1">
            <span></span>
            <p>没有拿到早餐</p>
        </li>
        <li values="2">
            <span></span>
            <p>早餐质量问题</p>
        </li>
        <li values="3">
            <span></span>
            <p>其他</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <input type="text" id="refundRemark" placeholder="您可以告知我们详细情况么？" class="text_input">

    <div class="file_box">
        <div class="wrap" id="imagePreview">
            <p>+ 点击添加图片</p>
        </div>
        <form name="uploadForm">
            <input id="imageInput" type="file" name="myPhoto" onchange="loadImageFile();" class="file_input">
            <input type="hidden" id="fileSrc" value=""/>
        </form>
        <span>*如果是质量问题，上传图片将帮助您更快解决问题</span>
    </div>
    <input type="button" id="submitBtn" class="button" value="提交">
</div>
<script src="js/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="js/layer.js"></script>
<script src="js/upload.js"></script>
<script src="js/apply_refund.js"></script>
</body>
</html>